训练：

nohup env CUDA_VISIBLE_DEVICES=1 python -u scripts/train.py --train_csv ../data_process/dta_data/train_pic50.csv --valid_csv ../data_process/dta_data/val_pic50.csv --test_csv ../data_process/dta_data/test_pic50.csv --out_dir outputs/run2 >train1.log 2>&1 &

change seed can repeate run 

推理：

python scripts/inference.py \
    --pairs_csv ../data_process/dta_data/test_pic50.csv \
    --checkpoint outputs/run2/best_model.pt \
    --prot_dir data/kdbnet/proteins \
    --drug_dir data/kdbnet/drugs \
    --label_col label \
    --out_csv predictions.csv
